description: You can use this app to search for houses to buy or rent in your area. All you need to do is sign up and link your account to Voiceter Pro. You can also get in touch with a local real estate agent so that they can help sell your house! Once you have finished the search with Alexa check the Voiceter Pro Real Estate app for the rest of your result.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask Real Estate to find me a home.
Alexa, tell Real Estate to sell my house.
name: Real Estate
shortDescription: An app where you can search for houses to buy and rent, and get in touch with local real estate agents.
vendorName: Tech Valley Homes Real Estate LLC
